Package: gloss
Title: Interactive Web Widgets for Vellum Scenes
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("David", "Schoch", , "david.schoch@cynkra.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Turns a 'vellum' scene (or a 'quill' plot) into a self-contained,
    client-side interactive HTML widget: hover tooltips and highlighting, click
    selection, rectangular brush-select, pan/zoom, and a toolbar -- driven by the
    per-element data keys, bounding boxes, and 'scene_model()' metadata that
    'vellum' emits. Requires no Shiny and no server round-trip. Named after the
    manuscript gloss -- an annotation revealed on the page.
